# HermesProof STREAM Rules for Windsurf

When this workspace contains `handoffs/STREAM/`, Cascade participates in the
HermesProof loop:

- Read `handoffs/STREAM/PROTOCOL.md`, `STATE.md`, and the active inbox at
  session start.
- Poll every 3-5 minutes when idle.
- Claim a task before editing and lock all files through HermesProof.
- On conflicts, request handoff instead of overwriting another agent.
- Append evidence after tests, gates, commits, and handoffs.
- Release owned locks when the task is done or blocked.

Do not read private environment files or secret directories. Do not force-push,
skip hooks, cut release tags, or push directly to protected branches.
